sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant UI as Browser UI
    participant API as /api/tori/stream (SSE)
    participant Limit as checkLimit()
    participant Ctx as Context Loaders
    participant Prompt as Prompt Assembly
    participant Safety as safety-classifier.ts
    participant LLM as tori-llm.ts callLLM()
    participant Provider as Anthropic / OpenAI / Gemini
    participant DB as Database

    Student->>UI: Types message, hits send
    UI->>API: POST (SSE) { message, surface, projectId? }

    API->>DB: requireUser() — verify session
    DB-->>API: session.user

    API->>Limit: checkLimit(userId, AI_REQUEST)
    Limit->>DB: SELECT UsageCounter WHERE userId + metric + periodKey
    DB-->>Limit: { count, limit }
    alt limit exceeded
        Limit-->>API: { ok: false }
        API-->>UI: 429 Too Many Requests
        UI-->>Student: "You've reached your AI limit for this month"
    end

    par Load context in parallel
        API->>Ctx: buildGlobalContext(userId) or buildProjectContext(projectId)
        and
        API->>Ctx: buildToriPersonalContext(userId)
        and
        API->>Ctx: UserToriProfile + toriContext + birthday + timezone
        and
        API->>DB: Load accommodation (StudentAccommodation if student)
    end
    DB-->>Ctx: Context data
    Ctx-->>API: Assembled context JSON

    API->>Prompt: Build system prompt
    Note over Prompt: tori-identity-prelude.ts<br/>tori-personality.ts<br/>TODAY IS {ISO date}<br/>User profile + context<br/>Accommodation adaptations<br/>Last N message history

    Prompt-->>API: systemPrompt string

    API->>Safety: regexClassify(userMessage)
    Note over Safety: Instant regex check<br/>SELF_HARM · ABUSE · THREAT

    API->>LLM: callLLM({ system, messages, model, provider, apiKey })
    LLM->>Provider: API call (streaming)
    Note over LLM,Provider: claude-sonnet-4-6 (educator)<br/>claude-haiku-4-5 (student/brief)<br/>User BYOK key if set (AES-decrypt)

    loop Streaming tokens
        Provider-->>LLM: Token chunk
        LLM-->>API: Streamed text
        API-->>UI: SSE chunk
        UI-->>Student: Streaming response renders
    end

    Provider-->>LLM: Stop reason + usage stats
    LLM-->>API: ToriLLMResult { content, usage, model, stopReason }

    par Post-call actions (non-blocking)
        API->>DB: recordToriRun({ userId, surface, systemPrompt, userPrompt, response, model, tokensIn, tokensOut, durationMs })
        and
        API->>DB: incrementUsage(userId, AI_REQUEST, 1)
        and
        API->>DB: upsert ToriUsageStat (content-free counter)
        and
        API->>DB: update ToriSession (engagement signals)
    end

    alt Safety regex hit → run AI classifier
        Safety->>LLM: aiClassify(userMessage) via Haiku
        LLM-->>Safety: { flagged, category, severity, reason }
        Safety->>DB: INSERT SafetyFlag (never blocks response)
        Note over DB: School admin reviews flag queue<br/>Student gets response regardless
    end

    Note over Student,UI: Private mode (SupportiveChatSession):<br/>No ToriRun logged<br/>No safety queue<br/>No ToriUsageStat<br/>Hard-deleted after 24h
